citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany an APHIS Official during the inspection process Wednesday
9/10/2025 at about 1:35pm. The inspector contacted the representative who had to go pick up time-critical construction
materials (unrelated to the licensed facility) and would not be available for the next 3 hours. Failure to provide access to
the facility, animals, and records for inspection could be a serious non-compliance of the AWA and regulations. Failure to
comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section
